                <p>The current<span class="font-weight-700"> Mavrick 440 </span>introduced a muscular, neo-retro roadster styling that was well-received. For 2025, the design philosophy is expected to shift toward greater refinement and a more aggressive, upmarket feel, moving away from the more rounded initial aesthetic.</p>
                <p><span class="font-weight-700">New Aggressive Styling and Bodywork</span></p>
                <p>While the core silhouette will remain true to its roadster roots, the 2025 Mavrick is anticipated to undergo several subtle but impactful cosmetic changes:</p>
