                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Tank and Panel Sculpting: </span>The fuel tank, a central visual element, might receive <span class="font-weight-700">more aggressive contouring </span>and sharper creases. New side panels could potentially feature redesigned air vents or mock vents to give the bike a bulkier, more substantial appearance, mimicking larger-capacity naked bikes.</li>
